bio: Race in the Nascar Xfinity series for @joegibbsracing 18 CA ✈️ NC 2020 truck series champion 🏆

social_posts.post_text: Got the win out at @millbridgespeedway today. Can’t wait to get the @bb_micros out this season. Appreciate everyone’s help over the off season getting these things ready!

“$1,899.95! We’ll cut you a good deal!” -@sheldoncreed 

@wheleneng | @whelenmtrs

Officially been married to my amazing wife for 1 year, axel and I can’t thank you enough for all that you do for us and put up with (race cars 24/7) cheers to the next trip around the Sun 🍻 💜. I love you @cami.creed! Also happy birthday to my sister @shelbylmagdaleno we love you to!

🚨Sheldon Creed bringing the west coast style🚨

We had a blast in the off season taking a trip to Beech Mountain! @premiermountainguides hooked us up with an awesome day shredding, skipping lines, and hanging out in the private lounges. Won’t be able to do it any other way! Thanks, guys! Such a fun group to hang out with!
Phoenix photo dump 📷- decent speed all day and was able to rebound from a late left rear flat/spin to a p3 finish.

Great first night in the new @bbracechassis . a couple new car bugs to work out but she rips!  @wheleneng  @bbracechassis  @khsuspension  @eibach_world  @adams_performance  @guhl.motors  @visioncanopies  @bellracinghq  @sparcousa

P3 at @millbridgespeedway last night, heat win and 2nd in the dash with another fast @bbracechassis , driver took to to long to get it rolling in the main but I’ll work on that for the future. Appreciate everyone help on the micro program! @whelenmtrs @bbracechassis @khsuspension @guhl.motors @adams_performance @visioncanopies @eibach_world @bellracinghq @sparcousa
•The Lady In Black• I love this place. Good speed today, rolling off p7 plenty of laps to dial her in tomorrow! @wheleneng @whelenmtrs @rcrracing
@bbracechassis out did them selves on this one, and to top it off she’s a ripper. #amaturemicroguy
One whole year with our little boy axel. This Year has been nothing short of amazing watching you grow, you have lit our house with joy and continue to amaze us. We love you axel!
Thanks for hosting us today, @wheleneng!
Great time visiting our friends at @wheleneng’s Connecticut facility earlier this week. Now it’s time to go racing at @nhms.
Ready to make my Cup debut. Thankful for the opportunity. Let’s get it!
